\fs32 \
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\qj\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs36 \cf0 In modern software development, the data models you work with are often crystal clear and well-defined. You\'92ve got a User, Tweet or Invoice object, and you know exactly what kind of properties it has.\
